{"tid":1684897,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Twitter稱無意進軍中國 希望用戶相信所看資訊","createTime":"2019-10-31T10:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T10:33:27.000Z","uid":68738,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8c310233545e44501f43adc9e1c21a55609213","tid":1684897,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2485000/2485264/20191029_16_v2_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2485000%2F2485264%2F20191029_16_v2_600.png&h=e6a8ff9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國社交平台Twitter（美︰TWTR）早前公布的業績遜預期，外界關注目前在中國被屏蔽的Twitter會否試圖開拓中國市場，尋找新機遇，惟Twitter財務總監西格爾（Ned Segal）表明，無計劃進入中國市場。<br />\n<br />\n西格爾接受CNBC訪問時表示，Twitter無意進入中國市場，強調希望用戶相信他們所看到的資訊，加入討論並覺得安全。<br />\n<br />\n西格爾稱目前的發展方向，是致力提升現有1.45億可獲利每日活躍用戶的使用體驗。<br />\n<br />\n廣告是Twitter重要收入來源，西格爾指Twitter正努力改變廣告形式，加強與用戶的相關性，讓廣告客戶的影片更能與用戶連結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2485264/Twitter稱無意進軍中國%20希望用戶相信所看資訊\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2485264%2FTwitter%E7%A8%B1%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E9%80%B2%E8%BB%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2520%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E6%89%80%E7%9C%8B%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA1R4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=e9c7599e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2485264/Twitter稱無意進軍中國%20希望用戶相信所看資訊</a>"},{"pid":"5ded15aae363d8bb0a2d75d5fc7c3b89674f12f2","tid":1684897,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZHCuMf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZHCuMf.jpg&h=0ecf3101&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3bb2597b4a1cbb5e4d82b8a233c416b788fe40d","tid":1684897,"uid":20870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:31:12